    "Cabin air is brutally dry — hands suffer first, and most people only notice once they're already cracked" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die Kabinenluft ist brutal trocken — die Hände leiden zuerst, und die meisten merken es erst, wenn sie bereits rissig sind"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cabin air is brutally dry — hands suffer first, and most people only notice once they're already cracked"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "El aire de la cabina es brutalmente seco — las manos son las primeras en sufrirlo, y la mayoría solo lo nota cuando ya se han agrietado"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "L'air de la cabine est terriblement sec — les mains en souffrent en premier, et la plupart des gens ne s'en aperçoivent qu'une fois qu'elles sont déjà gercées"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "機内の空気は容赦なく乾燥している — 手が最初にダメージを受け、ほとんどの人は荒れてからようやく気づく"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "기내 공기는 매우 건조합니다 — 손이 가장 먼저 고생하고, 대부분의 사람들은 이미 갈라진 후에야 알아채요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "O ar da cabine é brutalmente seco — as mãos sofrem primeiro, e a maioria das pessoas só percebe quando já estão rachadas"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "机舱空气偏干，手最容易先不舒服，提前护理会好很多"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "機艙空氣偏乾，手最容易先不舒服，提前護理會好很多"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cabin air is drier than most deserts — your nose bears the brunt silently. A few sprays keep things comfortable and meaningfully reduce that heavy-headed feeling after landing" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die Kabinenluft ist trockener als die meisten Wüsten — die Nase leidet still darunter. Ein paar Sprühstöße halten alles angenehm feucht und können das dumpfe Gefühl nach der Landung spürbar mindern"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "El aire de cabina es más seco que la mayoría de los desiertos — la nariz lo sufre en silencio. Unos pocos sprays mantienen la comodidad y reducen notablemente esa sensación de pesadez al llegar"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "L'air de cabine est plus sec que la plupart des déserts — votre nez en pâtit sans que vous vous en rendiez compte. Quelques sprays suffisent à rester à l'aise et à réduire sensiblement la lourdeur ressentie à l'atterrissage"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "機内の空気はほとんどの砂漠より乾燥しています――鼻が静かに影響を受けています。数回スプレーするだけで快適さが保たれ、着陸後の頭の重さが明らかに和らぎます"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "기내 공기는 대부분의 사막보다 건조합니다 — 코가 조용히 그 영향을 받습니다. 몇 번 뿌리는 것만으로도 편안함을 유지하고 착륙 후 머리가 무거운 느낌을 크게 줄일 수 있습니다"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "O ar da cabine é mais seco que a maioria dos desertos — seu nariz sente os efeitos em silêncio. Alguns sprays mantêm tudo confortável e reduzem notavelmente aquela sensação de peso após o desembarque"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "机舱空气比大多数沙漠还干燥——鼻腔是最先感受到的地方，只是通常悄无声息。几次喷雾能让整个飞行舒适很多，也能明显减轻落地后那种沉重感"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "機艙空氣比大多數沙漠還乾燥——鼻腔是最先感受到的地方，只是通常悄無聲息。幾次噴霧能讓整趟飛行舒適很多，也能明顯減輕落地後那種沉重感"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cabins can get warm, especially in tropical ports — a small USB fan is a real sleep improvement" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Kabinen können warm werden, besonders in tropischen Häfen — ein kleiner USB-Ventilator verbessert den Schlaf wirklich"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cabins can get warm, especially in tropical ports — a small USB fan is a real sleep improvement"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Los camarotes pueden calentarse, especialmente en puertos tropicales — un pequeño ventilador USB mejora considerablemente el sueño"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les cabines peuvent devenir chaudes, surtout dans les ports tropicaux — un petit ventilateur USB améliore vraiment le sommeil"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "特にトロピカルな港では客室が暑くなりがち — 小さなUSBファンがあるだけで睡眠の質が格段に上がる"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "특히 열대 항구에서는 선실이 더워질 수 있습니다 — 작은 USB 선풍기 하나가 수면의 질을 크게 높여줘요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "As cabines podem esquentar, especialmente em portos tropicais — um pequeno ventilador USB melhora muito o sono"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "热带航线舱内偏闷，小风扇常能提升睡眠质量"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "船艙可能很熱，尤其在熱帶港口停靠時——一個小USB風扇真的能改善睡眠"
          }
        }
      }
    },
