    "One evening, run a bath — it is a small decision that can make a whole trip feel like it was properly lived" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Einen Abend lang ein Bad einlaufen lassen — eine kleine Entscheidung, die die ganze Reise wie richtig gelebt erscheinen lässt"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "One evening, run a bath — it is a small decision that can make a whole trip feel like it was properly lived"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Una noche, date un baño — es una pequeña decisión que puede hacer que todo el viaje se sienta realmente vivido"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un soir, faites couler un bain — c'est une petite décision qui peut donner à tout un voyage le sentiment d'avoir été vécu pleinement"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ある晩、お風呂をゆっくり楽しんで。その小さな選択が、旅全体を本当に大切にされた時間に変えてくれます"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "어느 저녁, 욕조에 물을 채워 보세요. 그 작은 결정이 여행 전체를 제대로 살아낸 느낌으로 만들어줄 수 있습니다"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Uma noite, encha a banheira — é uma pequena decisão que pode fazer toda a viagem parecer verdadeiramente vivida"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "某个晚上，好好泡个澡——就这一个决定，能让整段旅程都多一点被好好对待的感觉"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "某個晚上，好好泡個澡——就這一個決定，能讓整段旅程都多一點被好好對待的感覺"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "One lightweight cloth that works as a beach cover-up, a towel, a picnic blanket, a makeshift shade, or a bag — it never takes up meaningful space and gets used every single day" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein leichtes Tuch, das als Strandkleid, Handtuch, Picknickdecke, improvisierten Sonnenschutz oder Tasche dient — nimmt kaum Platz ein und wird täglich benutzt"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Una tela ligera que funciona como cubreplaya, toalla, manta de picnic, improvisada sombra o bolsa — no ocupa casi nada y se usa todos los días"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un simple tissu léger qui sert de paréo, serviette, nappe de pique-nique, pare-soleil ou sac — il ne prend presque pas de place et s'utilise chaque jour"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ビーチカバーアップ、タオル、ピクニックシート、日よけ、バッグとして使える一枚の軽い布——ほとんどスペースを取らず、毎日使えます"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "비치 커버업, 수건, 피크닉 담요, 임시 그늘막, 가방으로 쓸 수 있는 가벼운 천 한 장 — 공간을 거의 차지하지 않으면서 매일 활용됩니다"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Um tecido leve que serve como cobertura de praia, toalha, manta de piquenique, sombra improvisada ou sacola — quase não ocupa espaço e é usado todos os dias"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "一块轻薄的布，可以当沙滩裙、毛巾、野餐垫、临时遮阳布，也可以当袋子——几乎不占空间，却几乎每天都会用到"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "一塊輕薄的布，可以當沙灘裙、毛巾、野餐墊、臨時遮陽布，也可以當袋子——幾乎不占空間，卻幾乎每天都會用到"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "One pair of dark trousers or a dark skirt — a quiet confidence on heavier days" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Eine dunkle Hose oder ein dunkler Rock – stille Sicherheit an schwereren Tagen"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "One pair of dark trousers or a dark skirt — a quiet confidence on heavier days"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Unos pantalones oscuros o una falda oscura: una confianza serena en los días más difíciles"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un pantalon foncé ou une jupe foncée : une assurance discrète pour les jours plus difficiles"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "濃い色のパンツかスカートを1枚。気が重い日にそっと自信をくれます"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "어두운 색 바지나 치마 한 벌. 힘든 날 조용한 자신감이 되어줘요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Uma calça escura ou uma saia escura — uma confiança discreta nos dias mais difíceis"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "准备一条深色下装，状态会更从容安心"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "一條深色褲子或裙子——流量多的那天的底氣"
          }
        }
      }
    },
