    "You will buy something at a market or deli — saves scrambling for a bag at the checkout" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Du wirst etwas auf einem Markt oder in einem Feinkostladen kaufen — erspart das Suchen nach einer Tüte an der Kasse"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "You will buy something at a market or deli — saves scrambling for a bag at the checkout"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Comprarás algo en un mercado o en una tienda delicatessen — evita buscar una bolsa a toda prisa en la caja"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vous achèterez quelque chose dans un marché ou une épicerie — évite de chercher un sac en catastrophe à la caisse"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "市場やデリで何か買うことになる — レジで袋を慌てて探さずに済む"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "시장이나 델리에서 뭔가를 사게 됩니다 — 계산대에서 허둥지둥 봉투를 찾을 필요가 없어요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Você vai comprar algo num mercado ou delicatessen — evita correr atrás de uma sacola no caixa"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "逛市集和便利店时很常用，临时买东西不用再找袋子"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你一定會在市場或熟食店買東西——免得在結帳時四處找袋子"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your phone will capture everything perfectly. Which is exactly why a disposable feels different — the grain, the not-knowing, the waiting" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dein Handy würde alles perfekt festhalten. Genau deshalb fühlt sich eine Einwegkamera anders an — das Korn, das Nichtwissen, das Warten"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Your phone will capture everything perfectly. Which is exactly why a disposable feels different — the grain, the not-knowing, the waiting"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tu teléfono capturará todo perfectamente. Por eso una desechable se siente diferente — el grano, la incertidumbre, la espera"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ton téléphone saisira tout parfaitement. C'est exactement pourquoi un jetable est différent — le grain, l'incertitude, l'attente"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "スマホなら完璧に撮れる。だからこそ使い捨てカメラは違う感覚がある——フィルムの粒子感、どんな風に撮れたかわからないこと、現像を待つ時間"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "스마트폰은 모든 걸 완벽하게 담아낼 것이다. 바로 그래서 일회용 카메라는 다르게 느껴진다 — 필름 입자, 모르는 채로 기다림, 그 기다림 자체"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Seu celular vai capturar tudo perfeitamente. É exatamente por isso que uma câmera descartável parece diferente — o grão, o não saber, a espera"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你的手机能把一切都拍得完美。正因如此，一次性相机才感觉不同——那些颗粒感，那种不知道拍成什么样，那段等待"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你的手機能把一切都拍得完美。正因如此，一次性相機才感覺不同——那些顆粒感，那種不知道拍成什麼樣，那段等待"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your trips will appear here." : {
