    "下大雨时把手机、卡和票据装进去，会少很多“怕淋湿”的焦虑" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bei Starkregen Handy, Karten und Tickets einfach reinstecken — viel weniger Stress, dass alles nass wird"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "In heavy rain, putting your phone, cards, and tickets inside removes a lot of avoidable stress"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Con lluvia intensa, mete dentro el móvil, las tarjetas y los billetes — mucha menos ansiedad por mojarse"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Par forte pluie, glissez-y téléphone, cartes et billets — bien moins de stress à l'idée de tout mouiller"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "大雨の時にスマホ、カード、チケットを入れておけば、濡れる心配をずっと減らせる"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "폭우 때 스마트폰, 카드, 티켓을 넣어두면 젖을까 봐 걱정하는 불안이 크게 줄어요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Na chuva forte, coloque celular, cartões e ingressos aqui — muito menos ansiedade de molhar tudo"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "下大雨时把手机、卡和票据装进去，会少很多担心"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "下大雨時把手機、卡和票據裝進去，會少很多「怕淋濕」的焦慮"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "公共洗手间和小店不一定随时有纸巾，这个小备份经常能救场" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Öffentliche Toiletten und kleine Läden haben nicht immer Taschentücher — dieses kleine Backup rettet oft die Situation"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Public restrooms and small shops do not always have tissues — this tiny backup saves the moment more often than you think"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Los baños públicos y las tiendas pequeñas no siempre tienen pañuelos — esta pequeña reserva suele salvar la situación"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les toilettes publiques et les petits commerces n'ont pas toujours de mouchoirs — cette petite réserve sauve souvent la mise"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "公衆トイレや小さな店には必ずしもティッシュがあるとは限らない — この小さな備えが何度も助けてくれる"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "공중화장실과 작은 가게에 항상 휴지가 있는 건 아닙니다 — 이 작은 여분이 종종 상황을 구해줘요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Banheiros públicos e lojas pequenas nem sempre têm lenços — essa pequena reserva frequentemente salva a situação"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "公共洗手间和小店不一定有纸巾，这个小备份很常救场"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "公共洗手間和小店不一定有紙巾，這個小備份很常救場"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "很小但很万能：晾湿袜子、封零食袋、固定小物件都很好用" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Klein aber universell: zum Trocknen nasser Socken, Verschließen von Snackbeuteln oder Befestigen kleiner Gegenstände"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tiny but surprisingly versatile: clip wet socks to dry, seal snack bags, or secure loose small items"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pequeños pero versátiles: ideales para tender calcetines mojados, cerrar bolsas de snacks o sujetar objetos pequeños"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Petites mais polyvalentes : pour faire sécher des chaussettes mouillées, fermer des sachets de snacks ou fixer de petits objets"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "小さいのに万能 — 濡れた靴下を干す、お菓子の袋を閉じる、小物を固定するのに最高"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "작지만 정말 만능입니다: 젖은 양말 널기, 과자 봉지 밀봉, 작은 물건 고정 모두 유용해요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pequenos mas versáteis: ótimos para secar meias molhadas, fechar sacos de snacks ou prender pequenos objetos"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
